parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the Classic Load Balancer (CLB) instance. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~2401682~~) operation to query the most recent region list.

parameters.name: ServerCertificateId
parameters.description: The ID of the server certificate.

parameters.name: ServerCertificateName
parameters.description: The name of the third-party server certificate that you want to upload. The name must be 1 to 80 characters in length, and can contain letters, digits, hyphens (-), forward slashes (/), periods (.), underscores (\_), and asterisks (\*).
